<a href="/articles/27197.html" class="com-grid-article" >
	<div class="grid-article-hd">
		<img class="pic lazyload" data-src="/system/articles/articleshows/27197/indexMediumPc2/27197.jpg?1463966539" alt="「票房」内地电影票房突破 200 亿，但别高兴得太早">
		
		<p class="category">
			<img src="/system/categories/iconwhites/3/medium/3.png?1411569578" alt="娱乐">
			<span>娱乐</span>
		</p>
	</div>
	<div class="grid-article-bd">
		<h1 class="smart-dotdotdot">「票房」内地电影票房突破 200 亿，但别高兴得太早</h1>
